<p>The <code>@current</code> property returns the current occurrence number (1-based index).</p>

<h2>Numbered List</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}@current{close}. {open}$name{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{users}
  {@current}. {$name}<br>
{/users}
</div>

<h2>Position Display</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  &lt;li&gt;Item {open}@current{close} of {open}@count{close}: {open}$colors{close}&lt;/li&gt;
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<ul>
{colors}
  <li>Item {@current} of {@count}: {$colors}</li>
{/colors}
</ul>
